<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:13:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列为期两天的约旦河西岸行动造成12名巴勒斯坦人死亡、25人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/12-palestinians-killed-25-wounded-in-israels-two-day-jenin-operation/0000018f-a536-df13-a3af-b536d3a80000</link><description>军方周二在杰宁市和邻近的城市难民营发起了这次行动，作为镇压该地区武装分子的一部分。巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战武装组织表示，其战士与以色列军队作战</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/12-palestinians-killed-25-wounded-in-israels-two-day-jenin-operation/0000018f-a536-df13-a3af-b536d3a80000</guid></item><item><title>谁害怕承认巴勒斯坦国？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/whos-afraid-of-recognizing-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-a496-d8a2-a3cf-a49735d50000</link><description>即使巴勒斯坦国是一个正在形成的“失败国家”，它仍然是以色列必须考虑的事情。你不能通过完全否定辩论和进程来塑造和影响辩论和进程，就像本杰明·内塔尼亚胡试图做的那样</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/whos-afraid-of-recognizing-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-a496-d8a2-a3cf-a49735d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内盖夫沙漠教堂发现早期基督教船只涂鸦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-23/ty-article/early-christian-ship-graffiti-found-at-church-in-israels-negev-desert/0000018f-a4ce-d639-a5bf-f7fe1d940000</link><description>在南部城市拉哈特的一个新社区的建设工作中，考古学家发现了六世纪的教堂，上面有可能将朝圣者带到圣地的船只的照片</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-23/ty-article/early-christian-ship-graffiti-found-at-church-in-israels-negev-desert/0000018f-a4ce-d639-a5bf-f7fe1d940000</guid></item><item><title>崩溃还是认可？巴勒斯坦领导人面临关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/on-verge-of-collapse-and-recognition-the-palestinian-leadership-faces-a-moment-of-truth/0000018f-a482-db21-a9ff-b4bec6b90000</link><description>欧洲国家承认巴勒斯坦国主要是对加沙局势的回应。但如果西岸的巴勒斯坦领导层不寻求变革，即使获得更多国家的承认也不会改变当地的局势</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:27:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/on-verge-of-collapse-and-recognition-the-palestinian-leadership-faces-a-moment-of-truth/0000018f-a482-db21-a9ff-b4bec6b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意对在以色列拘留期间死亡的加沙医生进行尸检</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-perform-autopsy-on-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody/0000018f-a494-dca3-a7cf-a5b542f40000</link><description>Adnan Al-Bursh 医生现年 53 岁，是六个孩子的父亲，也是加沙市 Al-Shifa 医院骨科主任。他的妻子亚斯明向以色列人权医生协会的代表提交了尸检请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-perform-autopsy-on-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody/0000018f-a494-dca3-a7cf-a5b542f40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员担心国际法院将裁定停止加沙战斗，准备实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-friday-on-measures-over-israels-military-offensive-in-rafah-gaza-strip/0000018f-a499-d639-a5bf-f7f90c950000</link><description>以色列官员担心，此前并未命令以色列停止加沙战争的国际法院可能会对以色列的军事进攻采取更强硬的立场，从而可能使其面临国际制裁</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 08:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-friday-on-measures-over-israels-military-offensive-in-rafah-gaza-strip/0000018f-a499-d639-a5bf-f7f90c950000</guid></item><item><title>被俘女兵的视频揭露了以色列10月7日最可怕的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-female-soldiers-exposes-the-most-horrific-failing-of-october-7/0000018f-a201-d5dc-a7df-eee7f4a50000</link><description>视频中最明显的事情之一是哈马斯绑架者的冷漠，他们似乎拥有所有的时间。那些对失败负责的人不能继续掌权太久</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-female-soldiers-exposes-the-most-horrific-failing-of-october-7/0000018f-a201-d5dc-a7df-eee7f4a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称有 30 枚火箭弹袭击以色列北部地区；以色列无人机在黎巴嫩杀死真主党官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-live/hamas-video-of-captive-idf-spotters-was-manipulated-female-soldiers-treated-ethically/0000018f-a31d-d476-a7df-e37d05110000</link><description>以黎巴嫩 ■ 数千人参加了在以色列国防军杰宁行动中丧生的 12 名巴勒斯坦人的葬礼</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-live/hamas-video-of-captive-idf-spotters-was-manipulated-female-soldiers-treated-ethically/0000018f-a31d-d476-a7df-e37d05110000</guid></item><item><title>被俘虏的以色列国防军观察员的视频更加证明了内塔尼亚胡的失败。他必须走了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-idf-spotters-is-more-proof-of-netanyahus-failure-he-has-to-go/0000018f-a282-d8ed-a19f-bec210410000</link><description>以色列总理继续用“全面胜利”的口号席卷公众，而视频中显示的以色列女兵仍被关押在加沙。他们的目光应该萦绕在他醒着的每一个时刻</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 23:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-idf-spotters-is-more-proof-of-netanyahus-failure-he-has-to-go/0000018f-a282-d8ed-a19f-bec210410000</guid></item><item><title>尼基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 抨击拜登因以色列暂停武器而“愚蠢”，并表示将在 11 月投票给特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/nikki-haley-slams-foolish-biden-over-israel-arms-pause-says-will-vote-trump-in-november/0000018f-a234-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7ad7b0000</link><description>美国前驻联合国大使、特朗普2024年初选最主要对手的背书，对拜登竞选来说是一个打击</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/nikki-haley-slams-foolish-biden-over-israel-arms-pause-says-will-vote-trump-in-november/0000018f-a234-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7ad7b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队在约旦河西岸杰宁袭击中造成 11 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/palestinians-report-10-killed-by-israeli-forces-in-raid-on-west-banks-jenin/0000018f-a08a-d35f-a1df-ffcbd2620000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦妇女在乘坐的军车碾压爆炸装置时受重伤；自以色列军队周二开始行动以来，拉马拉卫生部表示已有 25 名巴勒斯坦人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 18:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/palestinians-report-10-killed-by-israeli-forces-in-raid-on-west-banks-jenin/0000018f-a08a-d35f-a1df-ffcbd2620000</guid></item><item><title>面对女性人质的残酷镜头，以色列政府以无耻的傲慢回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-22/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-government-responds-to-brutal-film-of-women-hostages-with-shameless-arrogance/0000018f-a0cf-d639-a5bf-f3ffef930000</link><description>10月7日被绑架的五名年轻女兵的家人发布了一段被绑架的视频，希望唤起人们的羞耻感，以此作为唤起内塔尼亚胡政府良知的“最后手段”。至少一位利库德集团高级领导人显然没有这种耻辱</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 18:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-22/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-government-responds-to-brutal-film-of-women-hostages-with-shameless-arrogance/0000018f-a0cf-d639-a5bf-f3ffef930000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-combat-in-gaza/0000018f-a163-dff6-a9af-efebf1760000</link><description>他们被命名为军士长。 （res.）吉迪恩·柴·德罗（Gideon Chay DeRowe）、以色列·尤德金（Israel Yudkin）上尉和参谋长。埃利亚豪·海姆·埃姆萨勒姆</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 18:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-north-combat-in-gaza/0000018f-a163-dff6-a9af-efebf1760000</guid></item><item><title>建筑物被夷为平地，大面积破坏：这就是以色列在拉法的“有限行动”的样子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/this-is-what-israels-limited-operation-in-rafah-looks-like/0000018f-a063-d0e8-a79f-ac7b1e6f0000</link><description>卫星图像显示，占领拉法口岸后，以色列国防军沿着费城走廊向北推进，向拉法市中心推进</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 17:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/this-is-what-israels-limited-operation-in-rafah-looks-like/0000018f-a063-d0e8-a79f-ac7b1e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与共和党领导人接触，接受国会演讲邀请</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-engages-with-republican-leaders-to-receive-congressional-address-invite/0000018f-a11f-dff6-a9af-efbf4e080000</link><description>鉴于国际刑事法院检察官要求发出逮捕令，议长约翰逊敦促参议院领袖舒默邀请内塔尼亚胡。如果舒默不联署，约翰逊表示他将单独发出邀请，即使演讲​​只针对众议院而不是参议院</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 17:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-engages-with-republican-leaders-to-receive-congressional-address-invite/0000018f-a11f-dff6-a9af-efbf4e080000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普与拜登就以色列问题：为什么内塔尼亚胡应该担心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-v-biden-on-israel-why-netanyahu-should-be-worried/0000018f-a0aa-d5dc-a7df-eeef40820000</link><description>将唐纳德·特朗普最近对以色列的评论与乔·拜登的评论进行比较是值得的——因为如果你在没有附上任何名字的情况下阅读这些评论，你可能会把最亲以色列的话归咎于错误的总统候选人</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-v-biden-on-israel-why-netanyahu-should-be-worried/0000018f-a0aa-d5dc-a7df-eeef40820000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属播放的镜头显示哈马斯恐怖分子绑架以色列女兵进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/hostages-families-air-footage-showing-hamas-abducting-israeli-women-soldiers-into-gaza/0000018f-a0f2-d4c6-a5cf-f2f773060000</link><description>据人质家属称，这段视频时长仅三分多钟，经过剪辑和删除，删除了任何过于血腥的内容。它被哈马斯恐怖分子携带的随身摄像机捕捉到</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 16:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/hostages-families-air-footage-showing-hamas-abducting-israeli-women-soldiers-into-gaza/0000018f-a0f2-d4c6-a5cf-f2f773060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 229 天：内塔尼亚胡表示以色列无意重新安置加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-229-netanyahu-says-israel-has-no-intention-of-resettling-gaza/0000018f-a0fc-dff6-a9af-eefee5b70000</link><description>挪威、爱尔兰和西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国，以色列召回特使进行磋商 ■ 以色列总检察长称，国际刑事法院检察官要求对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特发出逮捕令是“毫无根据的” ■ 斯莫特里奇表示，他不会转移为巴勒斯坦权力机构征收的税款直到另行通知为止” ■ 据报道，以色列和哈马斯之间的停战谈判因埃及秘密更改协议条款而破裂 ■ 这是战争开始 229 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:58:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-229-netanyahu-says-israel-has-no-intention-of-resettling-gaza/0000018f-a0fc-dff6-a9af-eefee5b70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长向承认巴勒斯坦的国家表示：“从河到海只有以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-to-nations-recognizing-palestine-only-israel-from-river-to-sea/0000018f-a0fc-d4c6-a5cf-f2fd3d0c0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，埃里·科恩部长强烈主张使用武力解救人质，包括全面入侵拉法</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-to-nations-recognizing-palestine-only-israel-from-river-to-sea/0000018f-a0fc-d4c6-a5cf-f2fd3d0c0000</guid></item><item><title>AG：国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的指控“毫无根据”；以色列考虑进行国家调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/ag-icc-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant-are-baseless-israel-mulls-state-inquiry/0000018f-a0c7-d60a-a9ef-f1ef24ea0000</link><description>总检察长表示，国际刑事法院无权对加沙战争期间可能犯下的战争罪进行调查；以色列对其在加沙的行动进行彻底、真正的调查可能会导致国际刑事法院暂停自己的调查</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/.premium/ag-icc-warrants-against-netanyahu-gallant-are-baseless-israel-mulls-state-inquiry/0000018f-a0c7-d60a-a9ef-f1ef24ea0000</guid></item></channel></rss>